  "id": "LgWnS0yB",
  "slug": "variant-vanilla-blocks",
  "title": "Variant Vanilla Blocks",
  "description": "Vanilla blocks recreated in all vanilla wood types",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LJSiavZ.png\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Introducing '<strong>Variant Vanilla Blocks</strong>,' a delightful addition to the Minecraft universe that pays homage to the diversity of wood types found within the game. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">This mod is a celebration of the unique qualities each wood type brings, as it imbues familiar vanilla blocks with distinct styles that match the aesthetics of different woods. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">From the rustic charm of Oak to the deep hues of Dark Oak, '<strong>Variant Vanilla Blocks</strong>' offers a delightful array of themed blocks, each perfectly in sync with the wood it represents.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">This collection includes a wide range of blocks, such as Barrels, Beehives, Bookshelves, Cartography Tables, Chests, Composters, and more. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">The crafting recipes have been thoughtfully adjusted to ensure that every wood type has its unique flair.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">But that's not all&mdash;'<strong>Variant Vanilla Blocks</strong>' also adds a touch of magic with 'un-crafting' recipes. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Want to revert your variant blocks back to their original styles? No problem! This mod's got you covered, ensuring that you can experiment and craft to your heart's content.<br /> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Dive into this enchanting world of variety and style with '<strong>Variant Vanilla Blocks</strong>,' where every block tells a story of craftsmanship, creativity, and endless possibilities.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6UHsUm3.png\" /></span></p>\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Adds a number of vanilla blocks styled with each vanilla wood type</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Includes the following blocks :</span></h3>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n<h4><br /><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Barrels</span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1113186447575498763/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<h4><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Beehives</span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1111951035112636476/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Bookshelves</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1145000393697407026/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Cartography Tables</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1110654599305625710/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Chests</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qqAFAsm.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<h4><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Composters</span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1113028818756698113/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<h4><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Chiseled Bookshelves (1.20 only)</span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1109783324035129344/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<h4><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Crafting Tables</span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1119590651382734908/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<h4><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Grindstones<br /></span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1113071417089597450/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<h4><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Fletching Tables</span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1117937470894522418/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<h4><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Lecterns</span></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1112502770960973854/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;Smithing Tables</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1144986985451233280/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;Smokers<br /></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1020675523015356467/1144987522573799434/image.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">All blocks provide like for like vanilla functionality.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Recipes for the vanilla blocks have been amended to match the wood type, however 'uncrafting' for any variant block back to the original style has also been provided.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Each block type will <em>(eventually)</em> have a separate individual mod where additional support for modded wood is added, this mod is only for vanilla variants and will not change.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-beehives-fabric-quilt\">Variant Beehives</a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-barrels-fabric\">Variant Barrels</a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-bookshelves-fabric\">Variant Bookshelves</a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Variant Cartography Tables (TBA)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-chiseled-bookshelves\">Variant Chiseled Bookshelves</a><br /> <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-composters-fabric\">Variant Composters</a><br /> <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-crafting-tables-fabric\">Variant Crafting Tables</a><br /> <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-fletching-tables\">Variant Fletching Tables</a><br /> <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/variant-grindstones-fabric\">Variant Grindstones</a><br /> Variant Lecterns (TBA)</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"> &nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6UHsUm3.png\" /></span></p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<td><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/JMxYXtMz5r\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=452161&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"208\" height=\"50\" /></a></span></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/xanthian\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Github&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=452161&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"200\" height=\"50\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/xanthian\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Variant_Crafting/BH_VC_BisectPromo.png\" width=\"533\" height=\"80\" /></a></p>",
